The spawn is every 21 minutes in the king room in SolA.<BR>
King does not spawn every time, PHs can be a champion or a priest. There are 3 spawns in the room, a mage, a champion, and the king/PH. King only dropped this item once in about 4+ hours, it's the rare loot. The common is a ring of some sort (can't remember but I know that we gave them to the monks in the group)We had a full group of lvl 30ish people and a wizzy that was helping with blasts here and there not in group. <BR>
