<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Riggors Mortus</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-11-19 15:35:41</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Camped king last night.  Not too hard, the mage and the champions are tougher me thinks.<BR>
<BR>
Dropped ring of the golbin lords (ac5, str int 3 me thinks) three times and dropped the scepter once.  I lost on the scepter which looks neat.<BR>
<BR>
The king spawns in the bedroom antechamber not the throne room.  There is a new spawn in the throne room for a cleric epic quest (lord gimbo or somethun) but we got the place holder 5 times for that one b4 we left (large fire gob or something).<BR>
<BR>
With a full group you can tackle the King and the torturer (jailer) who is nearby and has cool loot but is a o'so rare spawn.<BR>
<BR>
Just clear out everything and you be fine, spawn rate is fair but if you get more than 3 or 4 mobbies you better know where the exit is.<BR>
<BR>
Riggs</font></td></tr></table>
